premise_source_doc_sentence: Jennifer Kent is an Australian actress , writer and director , best known for her horror film The Babadook  (  2014  )  , which was her directorial debut .
The Babadook is a 2014 Australian-Canadian psychological horror film written and directed by Jennifer Kent in her directorial debut , and produced by Kristina Ceyton and Kristian Moliere .
